node.title: Three injured in Auckland CBD shooting
node.description: Three people were taken to hospital early this morning after a shooting in central Auckland.
node.content:
["Three people were taken to hospital early this morning after a shooting in central Auckland.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Police were called to Fort Street at about 1.45am after reports of a firearm being discharged.", "The trio were taken to hospital, two with serious injuries and one with moderate.", "An 18-year-old man will appear in Auckland District Court today, charged with wounding with intent to cause grievous bodily harm."]
